menu "Example Configuration"

    config EXAMPLE_ENABLE_POWER_SAVE
        bool "Enable automatic deep sleep power save"
        default y if IDF_TARGET_ESP32P4
        default n
        help
            Enable automatic deep sleep timer management based on WebRTC peer connections.
            When enabled, the device will automatically enter deep sleep after all peer
            connections are closed and no activity is detected for a configured timeout.

            This feature is only available for ESP32-P4 target.

endmenu
